Package: shinyReports
Title: R Markdown HTML Tab Rendering for Shiny
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Sadler", , "alexander@apexomic.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simplifies automatic HTML report rendering from R Markdown reports in Shiny applications. Provides a UI element to trigger .Rmd rendering and displays the result in a new tab; opened automatically.
